  <objective>This project aims to contribute to individual well-being by offering a device that adapts music to the user's emotions. ONTBO is a software coupled with neurotechnology that detects, interprets and adapts audio content to human emotions in real time. ONTBO measures the emotional state in real time (concentration, stress, relaxation) thanks to a connected headset with an electroencephalogram. The various AIs will then deliver the appropriate playlists to enable the user to reach the desired emotional state.</objective>
